@Luap99,  the suggestion to remove the network options from the pod completely breaks my `MapSpec` approach. This would require a pretty big rework of this PR. The only issue I see with the duplicated net is for the libpod endpoint so can I just remove the JSON tags?

EDIT: Also breaks `Validate()` for PodSpecGen

Looking at it now actually, the `MapSpec` function will override the infra container's NetOptions passed in manually by the libpod API so we do not have to worry about different net options at all.
